title: PUSHIN P WITH CHARLY JORDAN — BFFs EP. 63
description:
We’re joined by Charly Jordan to talk about what she’s been up to since we’ve last had her on, the Sienna/Jack situation, and teach Dave about what it means to be "pushing P."
